AUDIOANALYTICSD(8) System Manager's Manual AUDIOANALYTICSD(8)

NAME

audioanalyticsd — Audio Diagnostics and Usage Reporting

DESCRIPTION

audioanalyticsd is a launch agent that aggregates and analyzes audio usage data for users that have opted in for reporting.

There are no configuration options to audioanalyticsd, and users should not run audioanalyticsd manually.
